HAWAII.
RANDOM COPIES OF THE 10TH EDITION OF THE CHART 19002
DATED 29 APR 2006 HAVE BEEN FOUND DEFECTIVE. THE
SUBMARINE TRANSIT LANES (ALOHA AND HULA) MAY BE OUT
OF POSITION. DEFECTIVE CHARTS DEPICT THESE SUBMARINE
TRANSIT LANES OVER LAND. THE 11TH EDITION OF CHART
19002 IS NOW IN PRODUCTION AND WILL SOON BE RELEASED.
MARINERS ARE ADVISED TO EXERCISE EXTREME CAUTION WHEN
USING THE SUBMARINE TRANSIT LANES ON THE 10TH EDITION
OF CHART 19002. FOR MORE INFORMATION CONTACT THE
MARITIME DOMAIN AT PHONE: 301 227 3147 OR 800 362 6289,
DSN: 287 3147, E-MAIL: NAVSAFETY@NGA.MIL.
